                        <i class="bi bi-mortarboard fs-2 text-primary"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Elite Tutoring</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted small">Scheduling tools, student portals, and course management for independent educators and learning centers.</p>
